| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-3110 — Mass File Rename (clop)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: b84c554a-02aa-5026-85f7-abe4e48308ee"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
